# Qwen3 model weights are stored split across vendor/qwen3-safetensors/
# (each piece <2 GiB, the GitHub LFS per-file ceiling) and reassembled
# into the FChatRAG resource bundle at build time by make-app.sh.
# The reassembled blob is treated as a build artefact, not source.
Sources/FChatRAG/Resources/Qwen3-Embedding-4B-4bit-DWQ/model.safetensors

